query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from tag_question AS tq
inner join question AS q
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.favorite_count >= 0 AND q.favorite_count <= 1
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('aggregate',
'artificial-intelligence',
'coldfusion',
'duplicates',
'interface-builder',
'jasper-reports',
'maven-2',
'qml',
'ssl-certificate',
'tags',
'windows-8',
'windows-installer',
'windows-services',
'xampp',
'youtube-api');
